(45, 1, '2013-12-22 00:46:42', '2013-12-22 00:46:42', '<strong>Background</strong>\r\n\r\n<b></b><i>Entrepreneur, Author &amp; Peak Performance Strategist</i>\r\n\r\nFor the past decade and a half, Manny Garcia has served as an advisor to business leaders around the country. Garcia is recognized as an authority on the psychology of leadership, negotiations, organizational turnaround, team building, life coaching and peak performance training, and has been honored numerous times for his strategic intellect and humanitarian endeavors. His nonprofit assistance to The Haven House for abused children and other non-profit organizations has directly impacted the lives of hundreds of abused &amp; sick children through both personal contributions and team based fund raising events.\r\n\r\nWhat began as a young person’s desire to help individuals transform the quality of their lives has grown into Garcia’s lifelong crusade as he is called upon for both business and personal growth strategies.  As a life coach, writer, business owner and speaker, Garcia has produced numerous publications, started a financial service company with fifty thousand dollars and grossed over five million dollars in sales his first year, served as a regular guest speaker on Heart Beat radio for woman, and is currently the President of Manny Garcia Companies, Inc overseeing three private companies and provides consulting services for numerous other companies.  Garcia is also acclaimed as a legend within the Vacation Ownership Industry having served as one of the youngest &amp; most successful Sales Leaders within Starwood Hotels &amp; Resorts World Wide, Inc.  For over a decade, Garcia ran one of the largest Timeshare companies in the world while exceeding budgeted sales of ninety five million dollars annually totaling over one billion dollars in sales.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Specialization</strong>\r\n\r\nManny focuses on global sales development strategies, lead generation, international team trainings, customer service experience and all recruiting efforts for Bric Realty, LLC.  His main goal is to ensure that global branding and customer service expectations  are exceeded while establishing international distribution channels for all of Bric’s inventory.', 'Manny Garcia', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'manny-garcia', '', '', '2013-12-22 00:52:03', '2013-12-22 00:52:03', '', 0, 'http://64.31.16.146/~bricreal/wp/?post_type=agent&#038;p=45', 0, 'agent', '', 0),
